  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个安全消息传输的时序图，场景是医疗科技领域的EMR同步。核心流程是：Aplicación发起请求，经过Sesión A加密签名，再传给Sesión B验证解密，最后通知Listener B。关键是每一步都要体现HIPAA合规的加密细节。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Aplicación",
        "Sesión A",
        "Sesión B",
        "Listener B",
        "HealthTech_HIPAA_Vault",
        "HealthTech_EMR_Sync"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了，医疗场景。我确认一下参与者设置：四个主体——App作为客户端，两个会话节点SessionA和SessionB负责加解密，ListenerB作为最终接收方。这样分层是否符合你们的架构？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Aplicación",
        "Sesión A",
        "Sesión B",
        "Listener B"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对的，但SessionA和SessionB要标注为\"Sesión A\"和\"Sesión B\"，ListenerB显示为\"Listener B\"。另外App要显示为\"Aplicación\"。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Aplicación",
        "Sesión A",
        "Sesión B",
        "Listener B"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已调整参与者标签。现在开始画第一条消息：App调用message_peer访问HealthTech_HIPAA_Vault获取密钥，对吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Aplicación",
        "Sesión A",
        "HealthTech_HIPAA_Vault",
        "message_peer"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "是的，然后SessionA本地执行三步操作：先用AES-256-GCM加密，再用Ed25519签名，最后加上二进制协议头。这三步都是SessionA自己完成的，不需要发消息出去。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Sesión A",
        "cifrar con AES-256-GCM",
        "firmar con Ed25519",
        "añadir cabecera de protocolo binario"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "收到，SessionA的三步自处理。接下来是TCP连接发送加密消息到SessionB，然后SessionB做验证和解密——验证Ed25519签名、AES-256-GCM解密，顺序没错吧？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Sesión A",
        "Sesión B",
        "Conexión TCP + mensaje cifrado",
        "Verificar firma Ed25519",
        "descifrar con AES-256-GCM"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "顺序对了，但注意SessionB验证和解密也是本地操作。最后一步是SessionB通过peer_messaged回调通知ListenerB，触发HealthTech_EMR_Sync业务处理。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Sesión B",
        "Listener B",
        "peer_messaged",
        "HealthTech_EMR_Sync"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "完整流程已绘制完成。我检查一下：App→SessionA获取密钥，SessionA加密签名加协议头，TCP传给SessionB，SessionB验证解密，最后peer_messaged通知ListenerB触发EMR同步。所有加密算法和回调都对应上了。",
